# Deploy

- DaemonSet for node-level DCGM/exporter; Deployment for operator control plane.
- Keep ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, and Binding in one place per component under `deploy/manifests/`.
- Document required labels/taints the operator sets so schedulers stay consistent.
- Use namespaced resources by default; cluster-scoped RBAC only when necessary.
